        "title": "Rank skills by installs and harden install telemetry",
        "body": "## Summary\n- rebuild the stale branch on current `main` with the focused install telemetry cleanup that is not covered by #2586\n- keep skill search popularity using stars plus all-time installs instead of downloads\n- add install telemetry dedupe by user, skill, root, and UTC day, with daily pruning and hard-delete cleanup\n- make telemetry clearing batch-safe and preserve fresh reinstall telemetry during an active clear\n- update API docs and the install telemetry/ranking spec to match the merged recommendation-score behavior\n\n## Removed after #2586\n- dropped the obsolete `recommended` browse index rename to install-rank indexes\n- dropped stale install-rank cursor/ranking tests now covered by #2586's recommendation-score path\n- removed unrelated CLI compatibility and publisher-abuse policy text from the new spec\n\n## Verification\n- `npm_config_registry=https://registry.npmjs.org BUN_CONFIG_REGISTRY=https://registry.npmjs.org bunx convex codegen`\n- `bunx vitest run convex/search.test.ts convex/telemetry.test.ts convex/crons.test.ts convex/skillStatEvents.test.ts convex/skills.exportList.test.ts convex/skills.banBatches.test.ts`\n- `git diff --check origin/main`\n",
